72bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f</data>
  <data key="d2">World Athletics Federation, also known as World Athletics, is a governing body that oversees global athletics events and record validations. It plays a crucial role in managing and regulating various aspects of international athletic competitions, including the prestigious World Athletics Championships. The organization ensures compliance with rules and regulations for these events, thereby maintaining standardization and fairness across different countries and regions where such championships take place. Additionally, it is responsible for validating records set by athletes during these global competitions, contributing to the integrity and reliability of athletic achievements worldwide.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees global athletics competitions like the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates athletic records.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773778969</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
