<node id="Splunk">
  <data key="d0">Splunk</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Splunk is a software platform that was upgraded from version 9.3.3 to 9.3.8 during the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk is a software tool used for monitoring and analyzing system data.&lt;SEP&gt;#Splunk是一个每周现场维护的工具或服务，涉及用户权限调整和其他维护操作。</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
