<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) is a relation describing a partnership where B人员 (personnel or staff member) provides comprehensive maintenance and service provisions to C客户 (customer). This relationship involves various tasks such as routine checks, repairs, system updates, and proactive measures aimed at preventing issues before they arise. The personnel of entity B consistently offers these services over a specified period to ensure optimal functionality and efficiency for the client's needs.

The relationship highlights a strong collaboration between B人员 and C客户, emphasizing a commitment to maintaining high standards of service delivery. B人员 executes multiple responsibilities including both reactive troubleshooting and proactive measures to ensure continuous operational readiness and support. For instance, B人员 performed maintenance on behalf of C客戶 for Splunk SIEM during the specified period.

B人员 is dedicated to providing comprehensive maintenance services that cover various aspects required by C客户 for their operational requirements. The descriptions collectively indicate that B人员 executes multiple roles such as performing routine checks, system updates, and handling reactive troubleshooting tasks alongside proactive measures aimed at preventing issues before they arise. These activities are carried out in collaboration with the customer to maintain high standards of service delivery.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员provided maintenance services to C客户.</data>
