<edge source="Tokyo" target="World Athletics Championship">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Tokyo hosts the World Athletics Championship, a significant international athletic competition where athletes from around the world compete in various track and field events. Tokyo serves as the designated host city for this event, leveraging its experience and infrastructure to accommodate the championship. The city's role includes organizing competitions across multiple venues, ensuring that the event meets high standards of organization and hospitality. Tokyo’s hosting capacity extends to managing international sports events, making it a suitable location for such prestigious athletic gatherings.&lt;SEP&gt;Tokyo is hosting the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Tokyo is hosting the World Athletics Championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Tokyo is the host city of the World Athletics Championship.</data>
  <data key="d9">event location,event venue,host city</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3</data>
