  <data key="d7">17.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, E客戶) refers to a relationship where C人員 is responsible for providing maintenance and service activities for E客戶. This includes executing specific tasks such as system maintenance, upgrades, and support primarily involving the Splunk system according to a specified work schedule. The engineer C人員 undertakes these activities regularly to ensure that the systems of E客戶 are well-maintained and functioning properly. On December 18, 2025, specifically, C人員 provided maintenance services for E客戶 as part of this ongoing relationship. E客户 relies on C人员 for such services, indicating the importance and regularity of these maintenance activities in supporting E客户的 operations effectively.

Maintenance work is carried out by C人員 based on documented tasks and a predefined schedule, ensuring that all necessary maintenance tasks are completed to support E客户的 needs comprehensively. These responsibilities include system upgrades, service execution during scheduled times, and continuous support for the Splunk software utilized by E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance services for E客戶's Splunk system.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员provides maintenance services to E客户including assistance with email suite installation and testing.</data>
