<edge source="C人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, C人員) refers to the relationship between a customer (B客戶) and personnel (C人員). C人員 provides various maintenance services for B客戶, including handling issues related to Splunk systems. Specifically, C人員 is responsible for providing monthly reports concerning Splunk usage to colleagues, which are relevant to the work done for B客戶. Additionally, C人員 acts as an assigned engineering resource for maintaining and resolving technical issues such as the Splunk Indexer queue full problem encountered by B客戶. This relationship encompasses multiple facets of maintenance activities, including routine checks, issue resolution, and ongoing support to ensure the smooth operation of B客户的 systems.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員collaborates with A人員to provide services at B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員assists A人員in providing maintenance and support services to B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員参与了B客户的维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance services to B客戶during the specified time period.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance services for B客戶involving a Splunk indexer issue.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员与A人员共同参与了B客户的驻点维护工作。</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer relationship,collaboration,communication,customer service,documentation,engineer involvement,handling engineer,involvement,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,service provider,service provision,support,technical support</data>
