<edge source="A人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人員, B客戶) refers to a relationship where A人員 provides maintenance services for B客戶. This relationship encompasses various aspects of system and on-site support for B客户, including tasks such as handling maintenance requests, conducting maintenance activities, and serving as an engineering resource. Specifically, A人员 performs maintenance tasks and provides on-site services directly at the location of B客户 to ensure their systems are functioning optimally. The maintenance activities carried out by A人員 involve addressing specific maintenance needs and ensuring that any issues with B客户的 systems are promptly resolved. Overall, this relationship is characterized by A人员 acting as a dedicated engineering resource for B客戶, fulfilling various maintenance obligations to support the operational efficiency of B客户's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is involved in maintaining and supporting B客户的系统.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is involved in the maintenance process of B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员负责对B客户的维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員handles maintenance for B客戶's system, addressing various aspects such as authorization and performance.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员负责处理B客户维护记录中的多项任务。</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer relationship,engineer involvement,handling engineer,involvement,maintenance,maintenance service,service,service provider,service provision,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede</data>
